<subSubSection pageId="94" pageNumber="694" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="94.[171,1378,722,1347]" pageId="94" pageNumber="694">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[173,526,1155,1189]" pageId="94" pageNumber="694">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Endangered on The IUCN Red List. The Shorttailed Talaud Mosaic-tailed Rat is known only from four specimens from twolocalities. Deforestation seems to be 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rummler" authorityYear="1935" box="[546,652,1238,1267]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Macruromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="94" pageNumber="848" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="major">a major</taxonomicName>
threat.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
